discern the frequencies that uplift or
weigh upon your spirit
imagine if you will a day bathed in joy
and serenity where your path crosses
with one clouded in Anger this
discordant energy unable to resonate
with your harmonious State simply passes
by leaving your peace undisturbed your
heart attuned to Love's frequency may
offer silent Compassion or choose to
gently steer clear of this
disharmony should a shadow within you be
touched by another's turmoil remember
you have cultivated the power to realign
with joy swiftly yet in moments where
your own heart is heavy you may find
yourself echoing another's discontent
amplifying the very feelings you wish to
transcend this dance of energies this
empathic connection to the world
highlights the importance of self-love
and acceptance especially in times of
inner tur oil by nurturing yourself you
attract Kindred Spirits those who
reflect your understanding and
compassion seeking the highest vibration
Available to You allows for divine

spirit and enhance your
journey in your interactions with the
world you will encounter those who
driven by fear May seek to impose their
views in ways that challenge Love's
presence recognized not as malevolent

part of the Divine whole yearning even
unknowingly for the
light it is not for you to dwell in the

direct your focus toward the light
within them offering prayers that one
day they may find their way back to the
radiance of their true essence
we urge you not to immerse yourself in
the lower vibrations of judgment or
retaliation Humanity's history of eye
for an eye has never cleared the path to
understanding or love instead stand firm
in the knowledge of your Divine Light
allowing your integrity and love to be
your
response when faced with unkindness
remember your essence you are reflection
of the Divine incapable of being
diminished by another's words or actions
your character your light does not
require defense for those with eyes to
see will recognize your
truth cast not your Pearls Before Swine
serves as a reminder that the
preciousness of your wisdom and truth
may not be appreciated by all your
energy your focus is better spent on the
love that guides you and the joy that
fuels your
spirit
in this time of Great Awakening you are
called to disengage from the energies
that seek to lower your vibration stand
in your light unwavering even in the
presence of those who dwell in
darkness let your love your joy and your
peace be your contribution to the world
influencing not through conflict but
through the sheer force of your
being beloved ones as you journey
through this life remember your focus on
love strengthens your connection to all
of creation it is in this alignment with
love that you find true power and
freedom I am Archangel Michael and I
bring you these truths so be
